      "title": "Home 1",
      "paragraphs": [
        "Welcome to Howrah Town Diabetes Study Society (HTDSS) website. Howrah Town Diabetes Study Society (Popularly known as HDS among doctor’s community) founded on July 1, 2018. Out of a thought- provoking idea to create a platform for education, enrichment and empowerment of doctors and the society in the field of diabetes, nine like-minded enthusiastic and dedicated doctors practising at Howrah having common interest in diabetes and its related specialities formed the first diabetes society in Howrah. To fulfill their dream two non-doctor socially active lady associates also join their hands. The aim of this group is to raise awareness about diabetes, conduct social and scientific programs to enhance learning, interacting and applying updated knowledge for the betterment of the society."
